{"tid":1897012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"弄跌市民身分證落渠　警致歉：清潔好後交還事主","createTime":"2020-02-25T13:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T18:01:58.000Z","uid":6497,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"94f3fcb68d4dbcad05dc917eee0419f98cc0e232","tid":1897012,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200225/s00001/d9f6de12c82a4679c517f3dc3ad884a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200225%2Fs00001%2Fd9f6de12c82a4679c517f3dc3ad884a8.jpg&h=a47e4a51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方證實，有警員向市民「抄牌」時，將市民身分證弄跌落坑渠。警方稱，已從渠中拾回身分證，清潔後交回事主，並向他致歉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人表示，警方今日（25日）上午約11時接獲市民報案，柴灣寶文街發生一宗交通意外。柴灣分區人員到場調查，其間人員不慎將一名司機的身分證弄掉到污水渠內。人員隨即從渠中拾回身分證，把其清潔好後交還給事主，並向他致歉。"},{"pid":"9eba9101a1d7de0bedf09a0103dc7cf6c5656fbe","tid":1897012,"uid":144541,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:03:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>人員隨即從渠中拾回身分證，把其清潔好後交還給事主，並向他致歉。</strong><br />\n<br />\n首次致歉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0125cbbb9f5aac792cd7d9ee3ec84cba4d9f851a","tid":1897012,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3285e08a7cb27689b4e9cd6945ec658a42ad3e","tid":1897012,"uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"等睇事主版本"},{"pid":"8f652a611602cacafa1f39e99423b8c78b419df9","tid":1897012,"uid":3270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d494ac18ee0d43201e0393c4a856f2ad2605129a","tid":1897012,"uid":109690,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係叫事主自己執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\"